           <email>byron.adams54@gmail.com</email>
       </maintainer>
   </maintainers>
    <release>
       <version>0.1.1</version>
       <state>alpha</state>
       <date>2006-07-11</date>
       <notes>- ssn :
                  - doesnt use PCRE any more.
              - region : 
                  - now support region names aswell as codes
                  - now support for north,south,east,west and central sectors of regions ie : Central Otago
             - bankcode :
                 - doesnt use PCRE anymore
       </notes>
